						"description": "Fast autocomplete search for medicines.\n\n**Access:** `ROLE_DOCTOR`, `ROLE_ADMIN`\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- `query` (required, min 2 chars): Search term\n\n**Searches across:**\n- Medicine name\n- Generic name\n- Brand name\n\n**Returns:** Top 10 matches ordered by relevance (name matches first, then generic name, then brand).\n\n**Example Response:**\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Paracetamol\",\n    \"strength\": \"500mg\",\n    \"form\": \"TABLET\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": 2,\n    \"name\": \"Paracetamol\",\n    \"strength\": \"650mg\",\n    \"form\": \"TABLET\"\n  }\n]\n```"
					},
					"response": []
				},
